Yall had 53 melee so I think I have seen a similar problem before.<br>
Be sure to tell your Healers to make hotkeys:<br>
/target MA<br>
/target SA<br>
/target 3a<br>
/target 4a<br>
and that dshould be it. Assign which clerics to which tanks.<br>
Nobody else should get any heals.<br>
Have your druids start casting spam heal right before aggro and dont stop through whole fight. Have the clerics start CHEAL immediately and do not stop threough whole fight. Necro to manna dump to clerics. Nobody else should be getting healed at all. If even 2 of those tanks live, you will win period.  <p>~Avezes Oscuridad
