=#122950>(12/21/01 10:59:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub12.ezboard.com/ftorvonnilousgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4168.topic&index=11>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Nagafen last night (12-20-01)</span><hr size=1> As I've said before - getting Nag stuck in the door is considered an exploit. I'm not really sure how actively GMs enforce it on Torv but people have been warned/suspended for it on other servers. You aren't jsut carefully using the environment to avoid the AE - you are getting a mob stuck somewhere it can't move further down from to where it has people on it's aggro list.<br>
