<br>
I'm pretty sure it applies to any resistable spell. Tash isn't resistable, so I doubt the enchanter would have to be in melee range. But the slow likely has to be from melee range. If in doubt, have a shaman conduct some tests on the fire giants on the way in. I think you also have to be in melee range to cast on them? If the shaman can't slow them from across the room, it's unlikely he can do it to Naggy either. <br>
<br>
Kriel<br>
