<br>
Tips<br>
<br>
Lvl is greater than resists but still unbuffed aim for a min 80 fire 80 magic.  Preferably 100 + in each unbuffed.<br>
<br>
In buffing, get the list set out previous and have buffing lines.  If you forsee having buffs fade before they are all finished have ppl camp out when fully buffed.  If you are having ppl camp out when buffed, buff them on a group by group basis and make sure they remember who is in whos group.<br>
<br>
X fingers that the login serverdoesn't go down when everyone is loged to chat and waiting the go ahead.<br>
<br>
I would say 3 50+ echanters minimum.  Though I have seen it lead sucessfull with less several times. <p>Tilian Down <BR>
